    {
      "id": "my_formal",
      "front": "my (formal)",
      "back": "제",
      "romanized": "je",
      "grammarNote": "제 = my (formal). 저 + 의 → 제 (contracted). Use with anyone you address politely — teachers, strangers, elders, colleagues."
